    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Auburn Bay</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A great place for outdoor enthusiasts, the community in Auburn Bay offers one of the most exquisite lakeside properties in this part of the town. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Designed with a cottage country-side character, the Auburn Bay Real Estate features marvelous green spaces and enormous parks. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">In addition to this, the community promotes a bevy of water sporting activities owing to its lakeside setting. </p>
